thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Jenny Darcy

author: Jenny Darcy
title: Jenny Darcy
text: Taxibox was reliable, helpful and the rates are very reasonable. They went out of their way to squeeze my redelivery in on a saturday that was already completely booked. Can't thank them enough and highly recommend their storage system.
